    "text": "UX Product Designer & Business Analyst | Bridging Digital Experiences, Gamification and Industrial Design",
    "links": [],
    "localImages": []
  },
  {
    "id": "28e3d5f4-a00c-8045-a7f0-fbb14a386870",
    "type": "sub_sub_header",
    "images": [],
    "text": "About me",
    "links": [],
    "localImages": []
  },
  {
    "id": "28d3d5f4-a00c-80e8-b262-ed1e2c00edf4",
    "type": "text",
    "images": [],
    "text": "Im passionate about projects that combine strategic thinking and creative problem-solving, especially where technology meets human behavior.",
    "links": [],
    "localImages": []
  },
  {
    "id": "28d3d5f4-a00c-801d-838b-ff7efb01995b",
    "type": "text",
    "images": [],
    "text": "Im a UX and Product Designer with a background in business analysis, gamification, and industrial design. Ive worked across creative, educational, and industrial sectors designing solutions that connect user needs with business goals and real-world impact.",
    "links": [],
    "localImages": []
  },
  {
    "id": "28d3d5f4-a00c-805e-84eb-fdc06cb0ece5",
    "type": "text",
    "images": [],
    "text": "My experience spans from game and learning design to industrial concept design, giving me a broad perspective on how people interact with both digital and physical systems. I enjoy transforming complex ideas into clear, engaging, and purposeful experiences.",
    "links": [],
    "localImages": []
  },
