  {
    "id": "2983d5f4-a00c-8025-bd58-f758255df0fc",
    "type": "text",
    "images": [],
    "text": "Product Description Decay is a narrative-driven survival & management game set in a dark medieval world. The project delivers mobile-first strategy gameplay with moral choices, systemic economy, and exploration, later expanding to PC/console.",
    "links": [],
    "localImages": []
  },
  {
    "id": "2983d5f4-a00c-8093-b588-faf8f7d237e1",
    "type": "sub_sub_header",
    "images": [],
    "text": "Project Files",
    "links": [],
    "localImages": []
  },
  {
    "id": "2983d5f4-a00c-80f4-ac25-c3b98668f095",
    "type": "text",
    "images": [],
    "text": "Business Analysis Plan I Case Study Documentation I Behance Documenation",
    "links": [
      {
        "href": "https://docs.google.com/document/d/1MJ7V4jpOxj-_vzXpU0pklFwasL8elmdxT1HwzeHDSOM/edit?usp=sharing",
        "text": "Business Analysis Plan"
      },
      {
        "href": "https://docs.google.com/document/d/15zeO6TtC_wGXV7k0uzWpwYxEMyE6AIz7vtqR_7jQCoM/edit?usp=sharing",
        "text": "Case Study Documentation"
      },
      {
        "href": "https://www.behance.net/gallery/233870289/Mobile-Product-Design-Survival-Game",
        "text": "Behance Documenation"
      }
    ],
    "localImages": []
  },
  {
    "id": "2983d5f4-a00c-8076-a896-ee6e45495873",
    "type": "text",
    "images": [],
    "text": "The initiative covers full-cycle production from business analysis and system design to UX/UI prototyping, core loop validation, and player testing.",
    "links": [],
    "localImages": []
  },
  {
    "id": "2983d5f4-a00c-80a6-95d3-c8ec984d7639",
    "type": "text",
    "images": [],
    "text": "My role: business analysis, gameplay system modeling, UX research, and interactive UI design (wireframes, usability tests, Figma prototypes, Confluence documentation).",
    "links": [],
    "localImages": []
  },
  {
    "id": "2983d5f4-a00c-80f8-ab87-d061ac62bb44",
    "type": "text",
    "images": [],
    "text": "Scope areas: market analysis, stakeholder mapping, process modeling, use case design, prototype validation, and iterative MVP planning.",
    "links": [],
    "localImages": []
  },
  {
    "id": "28e3d5f4-a00c-8098-b003-c55c7297d5e5",
    "type": "sub_sub_header",
    "images": [],
    "text": "Learning Managment System - Case Study",
    "links": [],
    "localImages": []
  },
  {
    "id": "2983d5f4-a00c-80ec-b796-d903bcbee497",
    "type": "image",
    "images": [
      "/image/attachment%3Af01a6889-5856-4b29-866f-abf9f9a74e4d%3A4c142db4-968a-4647-bf9f-e6a7c2dfe4b4.png?table=block&id=2983d5f4-a00c-80ec-b796-d903bcbee497&spaceId=30a3d5f4-a00c-81ee-bdab-000356588a34&width=290&userId=&cache=v2&imgBuildSrc=requestProxiedImageUrl"
    ],
    "text": "",
    "links": [],
    "localImages": [
      "images/02.png"
    ]
  },
  {
    "id": "2983d5f4-a00c-80a0-b60c-fe0ca4455fff",
    "type": "text",
    "images": [],
    "text": "Case Study Overview:",
    "links": [],
    "localImages": []
  },
  {
    "id": "2983d5f4-a00c-808f-a346-d18567290b4d",
    "type": "text",
    "images": [],
    "text": "This case study presents the business analysis process for designing a new Learning Management System for a professional training organization. The goal was to understand the companys operations, identify pain points in current tools, and define the requirements for a modern, integrated learning platform.",
    "links": [],
    "localImages": []
  },
  {
    "id": "2943d5f4-a00c-8095-9574-c4afbd8501bf",
    "type": "sub_sub_header",
    "images": [],
    "text": "Project Files",
    "links": [],
    "localImages": []
  },
  {
    "id": "2943d5f4-a00c-80e3-89bb-ec45a88c3729",
    "type": "text",
    "images": [],
    "text": "Case Study Documentation",
    "links": [
      {
        "href": "https://docs.google.com/document/d/1yZKA9m3UxxT4IYslVLQsFBzLTBvoIj95by8kfbIhqsM/edit?usp=sharing",
        "text": "Case Study Documentation"
      }
    ],
    "localImages": []
  },
  {
    "id": "2933d5f4-a00c-8053-ab25-fc73490b7aa5",
    "type": "text",
    "images": [],
    "text": "Problem Description:",
    "links": [],
    "localImages": []
  },
  {
    "id": "2943d5f4-a00c-80cb-b93f-efeb7c7f7d6a",
    "type": "text",
    "images": [],
    "text": "Course management relied on multiple disconnected tools, leading to data loss, communication issues, and lack of consistent oversight.",
    "links": [],
    "localImages": []
  },
  {
    "id": "2943d5f4-a00c-8009-8d45-df64de82933b",
    "type": "text",
    "images": [],
    "text": "Solution:",
    "links": [],
    "localImages": []
  },
  {
    "id": "2943d5f4-a00c-8010-b017-c45b215ddd3b",
    "type": "text",
    "images": [],
    "text": "A new integrated learning platform was conceptually designed through business analysis defining user needs, processes, and system requirements to centralize all training operations in one place.",
    "links": [],
    "localImages": []
  },
  {
    "id": "28e3d5f4-a00c-805e-b58b-c654ab74e874",
    "type": "divider",
    "images": [],
    "text": "",
    "links": [],
    "localImages": []
  },
  {
    "id": "28e3d5f4-a00c-8096-b2e2-e708d69c80c5",
    "type": "sub_sub_header",
    "images": [],
    "text": "Underground Garage - Released product",
    "links": [],
    "localImages": []
  },
  {
    "id": "2923d5f4-a00c-8053-830e-f0fbc090a97f",
    "type": "image",
    "images": [
      "/image/attachment%3Acb127c3e-32b7-4d96-a7e5-122b0854136a%3Aug_main.png?table=block&id=2923d5f4-a00c-8053-830e-f0fbc090a97f&spaceId=30a3d5f4-a00c-81ee-bdab-000356588a34&width=420&userId=&cache=v2&imgBuildSrc=requestProxiedImageUrl"
