  },
  {
    "id": "2923d5f4-a00c-8079-80dc-fc799a772afd",
    "type": "text",
    "images": [],
    "text": "Underground Garage is a realistic car repair and tuning simulation realseased on steam. Inspired by Car Mechanic Simulator, set in a gritty underground world. The game focuses on authentic vehicle systems, garage management, and progressive customization, blending technical precision with creative freedom.",
    "links": [],
    "localImages": []
  },
  {
    "id": "2933d5f4-a00c-80e9-8069-dabe142eb04f",
    "type": "sub_sub_header",
    "images": [],
    "text": "Project Files",
    "links": [],
    "localImages": []
  },
  {
    "id": "2933d5f4-a00c-8011-977c-eb958dceb6c0",
    "type": "text",
    "images": [],
    "text": "Project Sumary | Steam Product Page",
    "links": [
      {
        "href": "/p/1fd3d5f4a00c8089a1c1edb1cbfc5785?pvs=25",
        "text": "Project Sumary"
      },
      {
        "href": "https://store.steampowered.com/app/1452250/Underground_Garage/",
        "text": "Steam Product Page"
      }
    ],
    "localImages": []
  },
  {
    "id": "28e3d5f4-a00c-808d-a510-d8859c14707f",
    "type": "text",
    "images": [],
    "text": "Context: The project entered a recovery and redesign phase after a missed release, requiring rapid stabilization and redefinition of UX, systems, and production processes.",
    "links": [],
    "localImages": []
  },
  {
    "id": "2923d5f4-a00c-80ed-b26e-c658106e207c",
    "type": "text",
    "images": [],
    "text": "My role: Lead UX Designer / UX Project Manager / Business Analyst responsible for UX direction, delivery management, and cross-functional coordination. I defined gameplay flows, use cases, and MVP-based UX iterations, ensuring technical feasibility and design coherence.",
    "links": [],
    "localImages": []
  },
  {
    "id": "2923d5f4-a00c-808a-8e8d-c4ec792fb448",
    "type": "text",
    "images": [],
    "text": "Scope areas: UX strategy, mechanic system modeling, use-case mapping, process planning (JIRA/Kanban), UIengine integration, and iterative delivery validation through internal and beta testing.",
    "links": [],
    "localImages": []
  },
  {
    "id": "2933d5f4-a00c-80c4-ab74-ff2b3b1bc827",
    "type": "divider",
    "images": [],
    "text": "",
    "links": [],
    "localImages": []
  },
